body.description: Say Hola to My Friend Nina! Inspired by the hit kid’s show, CoComelon, JJ’s friend Nina is ready for playtime adventures! Nina is bilingual and loves sharing fun phrases and songs in English and Spanish. Press Nina’s tummy to hear her introduce herself with the “Hello Song” or sing along in Spanish to the “Learning Spanish ABC Song.” Nina even comes with her favorite animal, a bunny, attached to her arm. CoComleon fans everywhere will be excited to learn, play and sing along with their new friend Nina! Pair Nina with Bedtime JJ and My Friend Cody for the ultimate playdate with friends! (Friends sold separately)

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: About CoComelon Join JJ and his family and friends in the animated world of CoComelon! Whether at preschool with his friends, at home with YoYo and TomTom, or on adventures with his animal friends, JJ invites kids and parents to watch and sing along together! CoComelon: Where kids can be happy and smart! CoComelon My Friend Nina Doll, Soft Plush Body - Music, Sounds, and Phrases in Spanish and English - Attached Bunny Plush Included - Toys for Preschoolers Get to know JJ’s adventurous friend, Nina, with CoComelon’s My Friend Nina plush doll! Press Nina’s tummy to activate musical sounds and phrases in Spanish and English, including clips of fan-favorite songs, “Hello Song” and “Learning Spanish ABC’s Song”! Nina comes with her favorite animal, a bunny, attached to her arm. Expand the world of CoComelon at home by pairing Nina with her best friends Bedtime JJ and My Friend Cody (sold separately)! CoComelon's My Friend Nina provides the opportunity to learn Spanish and English, making playtime fun and educational. Discover how to sing the Spanish ABCs with Nina! Plus, she shares fun phrases in both English and Spanish. You can enhance your child's CoComelon experience at home by pairing Nina with her best friends Bedtime JJ and My Friend Cody (sold separately).

Fan Favorite Songs Listen to fun phrases and clips of the “Learning Spanish ABC’s Song” and hear Nina introduce herself in the “Hello Song.” My Friend Nina Add My Friend Nina to your CoComelon doll collection! Nina sings songs and says phrases in Spanish and English. Nina comes with an attached plush bunny, which is her favorite animal! Your little one can play and learn all about Nina and her world! More to Collect You can enhance your child's CoComelon experience at home by pairing Nina with her best friends Bedtime JJ and My Friend Cody (sold separately).

About Jazwares Jazwares, a subsidiary of Alleghany Capital Corporation, specializes in consumer products including toys, plush, action figures, collectibles and musical instruments. Jazwares’ portfolio includes a variety of dynamic licensed and wholly owned brands. With over 20 years of design, development, and manufacturing experience, Jazwares is a company with a progressive focus on identifying new trends and transforming them into high-quality products for consumers of all ages. Jazwares, which is headquartered in Sunrise, FL, has offices around the world and sells in over 100 countries. Since its inception in 1997, Jazwares continues to grow through the development of new products and the strategic acquisitions of companies like First Act, Russ Berrie, Zag Toys, Wicked Cool Toys and Kellytoy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars CoComelon JJ Musical Bedtime Doll – The Perfect Bedtime Companion for Kids!
reviews.reviewText: Rating: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐The CoComelon Official Musical Bedtime JJ Doll is a delightful and comforting companion for kids, making bedtime a soothing and fun experience.Pros: 1. Musical Bedtime Friend: This plush JJ doll is not just any stuffed toy; it’s a musical bedtime companion. When you press JJ’s tummy, he sings clips from the popular “Yes, Yes, Bedtime Song,” creating a soothing and familiar bedtime atmosphere. 2. Soft Plush Body: The doll is made from soft, huggable plush material, ensuring that it’s gentle and comfortable to hold, making it the perfect snuggle buddy for bedtime. 3. Includes a Small Pillow Plush Teddy Bear: The inclusion of a small pillow plush teddy bear adds an extra touch of coziness. Kids can have a mini teddy bear to cuddle along with JJ. 4. Kid-Friendly Design: The doll is designed to be kid-friendly, with no small parts that can pose a choking hazard. It’s safe for children of various ages. 5. Promotes Routine: The JJ doll helps in establishing a bedtime routine, making it easier for kids to wind down and prepare for a peaceful night’s sleep.Cons: 1. Battery-Operated: The doll requires batteries for the musical feature. While this is common for musical toys, it’s essential to have spare batteries on hand.In summary, the CoComelon Official Musical Bedtime JJ Doll is an exceptional addition to a child’s bedtime routine. Its musical feature, soft plush body, and inclusion of a mini pillow teddy bear create a comforting and enjoyable experience for kids as they prepare for sleep. While the need for batteries is a consideration, the benefits of this doll as a soothing and routine-promoting bedtime companion make it highly recommended for parents and caregivers looking to make bedtime special for their little ones.
